originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name, 
    t.title AS movie_title, 
    c.kind AS company_type, 
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ',') AS keywords,
    COUNT(DISTINCT mi.id) AS info_count
FROM 
    cast_info ci 
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id 
JOIN 
    aka_title t ON ci.movie_id = t.movie_id 
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id 
JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id 
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id 
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id 
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_info mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id 
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000 
    AND c.kind IS NOT NULL 
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, c.kind 
ORDER BY 
    info_count DESC, actor_name ASC

WHERE "production_year" > 2000) AS "t0" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t0"."id" INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t0"."movie_id" INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id"

GROUP BY "t1"."name", "t1"."title", "t1"."kind"
ORDER BY 8 DESC NULLS FIRST, 4) AS "t4"

FROM (SELECT "t1"."name", "t1"."title", "t1"."kind", MIN("t1"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", MIN("t1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", MIN("t1"."kind") AS "COMPANY_TYPE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ',') AS "KEYWORDS", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."id") AS "INFO_COUNT"
FROM (SELECT "cast_info"."id", "cast_info"."person_id", "cast_info"."movie_id", "cast_info"."person_role_id", "cast_info"."note", "cast_info"."nr_order", "cast_info"."role_id", "aka_name"."id" AS "id0", "aka_name"."person_id" AS "person_id0", "aka_name"."name", "aka_name"."imdb_index", "aka_name"."name_pcode_cf", "aka_name"."name_pcode_nf", "aka_name"."surname_pcode", "aka_name"."md5sum", "t0"."id" AS "id1", "t0"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "t0"."title", "t0"."imdb_index" AS "imdb_index0", "t0"."kind_id", "t0"."production_year", "t0"."phonetic_code", "t0"."episode_of_id", "t0"."season_nr", "t0"."episode_nr", "t0"."note" AS "note0", "t0"."md5sum" AS "md5sum0", "movie_companies"."id" AS "id2", "movie_companies"."movie_id" AS "movie_id1", "movie_companies"."company_id", "movie_companies"."company_type_id", "movie_companies"."note" AS "note1", "company_type"."id" AS "id3", "company_type"."kind", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id4", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id2", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "movie_keyword"
RIGHT JOIN ("cast_info" INNER JOIN ("movie_companies" INNER JOIN (SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"
WHERE "production_year" > 2000) AS "t0" ON "movie_companies"."movie_id" = "t0"."id" INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "t0"."movie_id" INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id") ON "movie_keyword"."movie_id" = "t0"."id") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "t1"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t1"."id1" = "s1"."movie_id"
